ureshii noni nani ittendarou  

00:23:09.700 --> 00:23:16.040
Tatlı vanilyaya  

00:23:09.700 --> 00:23:16.040
amai banirani  

00:23:16.370 --> 00:23:21.250
tuz eklemek gibi...  

